highlights.text: “ไฟเย็น” by YOUNGOHM has been on Top Songs Thailand the longest, at 969 days straight.
“OMW” by SA!NT and YUNGTARR is the highest new entry on Top Songs Thailand at #184.
Saran has the most spots on Top Songs Thailand. “รออยู่อย่างนั้น” is the highest at #35.
“Extraordinary” by Anatomy Rabbit is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Thailand, up 61 spots at #78.
